Anyone ever encountered broken navigation where instead of the nav, there is a message displayed: “this list contains non-list elements”?

I’ve searched the web and that phrase doesn’t even net any results.

It’s a client we picked up with a theme that has a hard-coded nav. I’ve combed through it, validated it, removed all cruft, but alas, no joy.
It's gotta be in the code somewhere, I would have to see the module code to see
